Package sbml2modelica.preprocessing

This package contains a set of classes defining methods for pre-processing operations on an SBML Model.

Package sbml2modelica.preprocessing Description

This package contains a set of classes defining methods for pre-processing operations on an SBML Model.
The pre-processing operation is needed since it transform the Model in some standard form which is much easier to handle when working with it.
The pre-processing operation also examine the SBML Model in order to find the (possible) presence of some unsopported constructs.
